metadata.name: Water copy
metadata.description:
Water copy.
Photography of the artistic project Post cards for nine songs.
The works of the project are made with a hacked digital camera, manipulated and subject to modifications that change the product for which they were created. However, this contrasts with the narrative sense of my action, which remains constant in the attempt to obtain previously thought and measured images. The subjects to be photographed are taken from the titles of a Hiroshi Yoshimura Music for nine postcards.
